Invocation Name: fit food pantry
des:
Provides answers to frequently asked questions asked Artie's Fit Food Pantry that is located on the campus of Scottsdale Community College.
The food pantry is a service provided to the students at Scottsdale Community College to help them with food insecurity. 
Ask Alexa and she will give you answers to the most frequent questions such where the pantry is located, what are its hours, phone number, how to get started and more.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
